headline: Max Levchin Elected to Board of Directors of The Coca-Cola Company
summary: ATLANTA, October 16, 2025--The Coca-Cola Company today announced that Max Levchin, a PayPal co-founder who went on to found and lead financial technology company Affirm, has been elected as a director.
